$ Perl module Email::MIME

gh|PerlModules|/Email/MIME/script.pl||

This script, when run, prints
code {
Subject : Hello, how are you            
From    : "Beleidigte Leberwurs" <beleidigt@nowhere.qqq>
To      : "Saurer Stein" saurer@stein.ppp>
Date    : Sun, 5 Dec 2004 15:36:34 +0400

-----------------------
Hello Saurer

How are you? 

Cheers,
Beleidigte Leberwurst
-----------------------
This message is going to be encoded in base 64
code }

